name: Gov. Henry McMaster
tweet: Agribusiness is our state's #1 industry and that is thanks to our hardworking farmers. I'm grateful for what they do for our state and country.   Happy National Agriculture Day!  https://t.co/3NQfI0GxIV

name: Gov. Henry McMaster
tweet: 44 years ago today you made me the luckiest man in the world. Happy Anniversary, @1stLadySC!  https://t.co/QdSKVY5Gbm

name: Gov. Henry McMaster
tweet: Today I officially filed for re-election to serve as your governor for another term and build on our successes over the last four years. For South Carolina, the best is yet to come.  https://t.co/rzgQpupnrz

name: Gov. Henry McMaster
tweet: Joined the team at Charter Spectrum in West Columbia this morning as they announced 350 new jobs.   Thank you, Charter Spectrum, for your investment in our people!  https://t.co/T0266olsxT

name: Gov. Henry McMaster
tweet: Our work together has been close and constant and his leadership has produced unprecedented growth and prosperity for all the people in our great state. I look forward to continuing our partnership through the end of this session.
